row.process:
:pset &AGENT# = get_var(VARA.RBA.CONFIG,NI2_FILE_AGENT,1) :pset &LOGIN# = get_var(VARA.RBA.CONFIG,NI2_FILE_LOGIN,1)
:pset &JSON_FILE_PATH# = get_var(VARA.RBA.CONFIG,NI2_FILE_PATH,1) :pset &JSON_FILE_PATH# = str_cat(&JSON_FILE_PATH#,"NI2_MIDDLEWARE_") :pset &JSON_FILE_PATH# = str_cat(&JSON_FILE_PATH#,&$RUNID#) :pset &JSON_FILE_PATH# = str_cat(&JSON_FILE_PATH#,".json")
!:DEFINE &STRINGS#, string, 5
:set &STRING# = get_var(VARA.TECHNICAL_FLOW.MIDDLEWARE.1,&ITEM#,1) :pset &JS_VALUE_ID# = STR_CUT(&STRING#, 7)
:set &STRING# = get_var(VARA.TECHNICAL_FLOW.MIDDLEWARE.1,&ITEM#,2) :pset &JS_VALUE_NAME# = STR_CUT(&STRING#, 9)
:set &STRING# = get_var(VARA.TECHNICAL_FLOW.MIDDLEWARE.1,&ITEM#,3) :pset &JS_VALUE_STATUS# = STR_CUT(&STRING#, 11)
:set &STRING# = get_var(VARA.TECHNICAL_FLOW.MIDDLEWARE.1,&ITEM#,4) :pset &JS_VALUE_DESC# = STR_CUT(&STRING#, 16)
:set &STRING# = get_var(VARA.TECHNICAL_FLOW.MIDDLEWARE.2,&ITEM#,1) :pset &JS_VALUE_INST_DATE# = STR_CUT(&STRING#, 21)
:set &STRING# = get_var(VARA.TECHNICAL_FLOW.MIDDLEWARE.2,&ITEM#,2) :pset &JS_VALUE_UPDATE_DATE# = STR_CUT(&STRING#, 15)
:set &STRING# = get_var(VARA.TECHNICAL_FLOW.MIDDLEWARE.2,&ITEM#,3) :pset &JS_VALUE_LIGHTSYSTEM# = STR_CUT(&STRING#, 7)
:set &STRING# = get_var(VARA.TECHNICAL_FLOW.MIDDLEWARE.2,&ITEM#,4) !:send_msg "&$USER#","&$DEPARTMENT#",&STRING#) :pset &JS_VALUE_SLA# = STR_CUT(&STRING#, 7)
:set &STRING# = get_var(VARA.TECHNICAL_FLOW.MIDDLEWARE.2,&ITEM#,5) :pset &JS_VALUE_MIDDLEWARESSOFTWARE# = STR_CUT(&STRING#, 7)
